name: Chesna Braker
content: Chesna Braker was a female individual who was a landlady on Coruscant. Arihnda Pryce confronted her for neglecting to repair a leaking pipe in one of her tenant Daisie's apartment blocks. Following a tense argument, Braker reluctantly agreed to fix Daisie's leaking pipe after Pryce reminded her to comply with Coruscant laws and regulations.
